OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby union captain
OL,7,FStuart Hogg has been given a five-year
OL,8,Fnon-harassment order and fined after
OL,9,Fbreaching bail conditions.
OL,11,FSentencing of the the ex-Scotland
OL,12,Finternational for a separate charge of
OL,13,Fabusing his estranged wife over the
OL,14,Fcourse of five years has been deferred
OL,15,Funtil 9 January.
OL,17,FHogg earlier admitted breaching bail
OL,18,Fconditions by repeatedly contacting
OL,19,FGillian Hogg in June.
