OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to a single charge
OL,7,Fof domestic abuse of Mrs Hogg when he
OL,8,Fappeared at Selkirk Sheriff Court on 4
OL,9,FNovember.
OL,11,FHe admitted shouting and swearing,
OL,12,Ftracking Mrs Hogg's movements and
OL,13,Fsending her messages which were
OL,14,Falarming and distressing in nature.
