OL,3,CFormer Scotland captain Stuart Hogg
OL,4,Cgiven five-year non-harassment order
OL,6,FThe court previously heard that he
OL,7,Fberated his former partner for "not
OL,8,Fbeing fun" after going on drinking
OL,9,Fbinges with his colleagues, and once
OL,10,Fsent more than 200 text messages in a
OL,11,Ffew hours despite having been asked to
OL,12,Fleave her alone.
OL,14,FHogg appeared at Jedburgh Sheriff
OL,15,FCourt for sentencing on Thursday 5
OL,16,FDecember.
